step.details:
Add these type exports: ```typescript export interface Organization { id: number name: string slug: string created_by: number | null created_at: string updated_at: string }
export interface OrganizationMember { id: number organization_id: number user_id: number role: "owner" | "admin" | "viewer" joined_at: string user_email?: string user_name?: string }
export interface OrganizationWithRole extends Organization { user_role?: "owner" | "admin" | "viewer" } ```
